Super-secret project, tinkering with lua and love.

Right now, it displays a simple simulation of our solar system.

Usage:  With love installed, CD to the directory and run "love ."
  See http://love2d.org/wiki/Getting_Started

Keys:
  Up/Down     - Zoom in or out
  Left/Right  - Accelerate / Decelerate time
  f           - Toggle fullscreen
  p           - Toggle planet zoom (show planets 1000 times actual size)
  r           - Toggle reticle (crosshairs) around planets
  o           - Toggle display of orbital paths
  q           - Quit
  shift 0-9   - Center on primary (0) or planet (1-9) of the solar system

Mouse:
  Left-click to center on a star or planet.
  Right-click to bring up a properites inspector for a star or planet.
